profile_positions.description:
• Led the initiation of e-commerce channel in Kazakhstan;
• Devised comprehensive e-commerce strategy over 5 years that include , that include conducting extensive market research;
• Developed joint-business plan for common growth in the channel for E-commerce clients;
• Negotiated with e-pharmacies and brick-and-mortar clients for successful implementation of strategy.

🎯 Key achievement:

• Implemented sales analytics system in E-commerce using BrandQuad analytics tool, providing real-time data on product availability, pricing of our and competitors' products, and alerting on competitors' discount activations;
• Developed FACE project, including Fix-the-Basics sub-project, aimed at improving basic tools for E-commerce.

• Developed and implemented tailored digital media strategy for target audience tribes;
• Analyzed sales and audience data from sources such as Nielson and internal BI department;
• Determined effective promotion methods for 7 brands across various digital channels (including SMM, digital media and paid search);
• Managed development of local advertising materials for all brands;
• Prepared and adapted creative assets (packshots, banners) and product information for E-commerce customers;
• Ensured visually appealing and up-to-date product listings to improve overall customer experience and drive sales through E-commerce channels.

🎯 Key achievement:

• Achieved a high average engagement rate of 7.2% on Prostokvashino's social media accounts by implementing a visual publishing strategy featuring only local people. This approach increased user engagement with content from people they trust within their communities;
• Launched a geo-targeted consumer awareness campaign in supermarkets and hypermarkets, using purchased cookie data to target shoppers who had previously purchased competitor products. This resulted in an overall increase in brand sales.

• Developed and managed two websites (https://lukoil-shop.kz & https://b2b.lukoil-shop.kz) for direct sales of motor-oil to customers and manufacturers;
• Developed a strategy for online sales, manually managed content and product portfolio on the websites, and implemented SEO;
• Promoted the websites with paid-search and developed a speech for external call-centre for customer support;
• Managed social media pages on Facebook and Instagram for daily customer communication;
• Conducted promotional activations and created content for social media pages.

🎯 Key achievement:

Managed and developed websites that achieved an average of ~6500 monthly visits and generated sales within two months of launch, resulting in the first sale of 60 tons of motor oil worth 16,500,000 KZT through organic search.

• Developed and executed marketing plans for the motor oil portfolio, including TV and radio advertising and BTL activities;
• Launched a new premium motor oil line, "Lukoil Genesis," nationally, including POSm support, TV and radio advertising, and dealer conferences;
• Conducted trade marketing activities for direct dealers in 21 cities across Kazakhstan, in collaboration with BTL agencies;
• Conducted the grand opening of the largest motor oil production plant in Almaty, including creating a creative concept for event, creating speech cards for speakers and press invitations, with participation from the President of Kazakhstan.
